about.description: Newly renovated, new management and perfect location at the junction of I-35, 290 & 183. Live only minutes away from shopping centers, Downtown, The Domain, Tesla, and Samsung! Starburst is an apartment community located in Travis County and the 78753 ZIP Code. This area is served by the Austin Independent attendance zone. Unique Features
